{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, after all, he doesn't believe in dreams, you know, either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's just something about this dream that he's very disturbed about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father said, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you are so worried about it, go to the treuhander, and perhaps-- perhaps he will let you go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See what you can do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sure that it is all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, you know, if it worries you to that extent-- and we went to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whatever he told him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, suddenly, there he is, in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a fright.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By seeing him, we got a fright, because he just went back three or four days before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, at that stage, everything was as it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you know, it seemed to-- sort of-- you know, every day with a-- with a missing, with this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were-- the three of us were together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, the other people, all of them, they didn't take away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Perhaps for the last few weeks they didn't take away the other people, either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just let them be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because, after all, they prepared for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so he said, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I think I just made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think if I go back now, I can come again for two days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Otherwise, you know, otherwise it will be maybe four weeks before I can-- I can come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, he felt perhaps silly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't tell us, but he must have felt silly then, at that time-- that moment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- so we said, OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can we go with you to the train?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know how it happened that the train went early.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
